snippet: Both golfers were at 10-under 206 headed into the final round of the first L.P.G.A. major of the season.
abstract: Golf Roundup; Michelle Wie and Lexi Thompson are atop the Kraft Nabisco Championship leader board in Rancho Mirage, Calif, setting up a possible final-round showdown that the LPGA Tour has been waiting for; other news noted.
lead_paragraph: Both golfers were at 10-under 206 headed into the final round of the first L.P.G.A. major of the season.

headline.main: Thompson and Wie Share Lead at Kraft
